 Kerala Education Rules, 1959-Provisions of Ch. XX, Ch.
 XXVIIA and XXVIIB are mutually exclusive-Teacher in aided school who has exercised option under r. 2 of Ch. XIV(c) is governed by Chapter XXVIIB- Cannot claim superannuation on basis of r. 8 of Ch. XXVIIA.
